<% layout("/layouts/boilerplates") %>
<style>
    .privacy-policy-terms {
        height: auto;
        width: 65%;
        border: 2px solid #cab1b1;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 4px 4px 8px  rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 3rem;
        transition: ease-in-out 0.3s;
    }
    .privacy-policy-terms:hover{
        box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(206, 70, 70, 0.549);
    }
    .privacy-policy-terms h3 {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .privacy-policy-terms h1{
        color: #ff6f61;;
    }
    .privacy-policy-terms strong ,.privacy-policy-terms a{
        color: #ff6e61cc;;
    }
</style>
<body>
  <div class="container mt-5 mb-5 privacy-policy-terms">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>At <strong>WanderLust Private Limited</strong>, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard the data you share with us.</p>

    <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>We may collect information when you create an account, post a listing, make a booking, or interact with our website. This includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Name, email address, and contact details</li>
      <li>Property details (if you host a place)</li>
      <li>Payment and transaction information</li>
      <li>Cookies and usage data to improve user experience</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p>We use the collected data to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Provide, maintain, and improve our services</li>
      <li>Facilitate bookings and manage user accounts</li>
      <li>Send important notifications or promotional offers (only with consent)</li>
      <li>Enhance security and prevent fraudulent activity</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>3. Sharing of Information</h3>
    <p>We do not sell your personal data. Information may be shared only with trusted service providers (e.g., payment gateways, hosting partners) under strict confidentiality agreements.</p>

    <h3>4. Data Security</h3>
    <p>We use encryption, secure servers, and modern security practices to protect your personal data. However, no online system is 100% secure, and we encourage users to take precautions when sharing personal information.</p>

    <h3>5. Your Rights</h3>
    <p>You can access, update, or delete your personal data anytime by contacting our support team. You can also opt out of promotional emails.</p>

    <h3>6. Updates to this Policy</h3>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be reflected on this page with the date of update.</p>

    <p class="mt-4">If you have any questions about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@wanderlust.com">support@wanderlust.com</a>.</p>
  </div>
</body>
